t-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- Quản trị kinh doanh, trợ lý, cố vấn</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- Kiến trúc sư, nhân viên kinh doanh</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">- Nghệ sỹ, diễn viên, đầu bếp, người trang điểm</span></div></span></span>','','2021-09-01 09:43:46',NULL,'{\"title\":null,\"desc\":null,\"content\":\"<p><\\/p><h2 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;\\\"><b>L\\u1edcI KHUY\\u00caN D\\u00c0NH CHO B\\u1ea0N:<\\/b><\\/span><\\/h2><span data-sheets-value=\\\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;L\\u1edcI KHUY\\u00caN D\\u00c0NH CHO B\\u1ea0N:\\\\nB\\u1ea1n v\\u1eeba \\u0111i qua t\\u1ea5m \\\\&quot;B\\u1ea3n \\u0111\\u1ed3 cu\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u1eddi\\\\&quot; c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh, hi\\u1ec7n gi\\u1edd b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u00e3 nh\\u00ecn nh\\u1eadn r\\u00f5 r\\u00e0ng h\\u01a1n v\\u1ec1 b\\u1ed9 h\\u1ed3 s\\u01a1 t\\u00ednh c\\u00e1ch v\\u00e0 ch\\u1eb7ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh ch\\u01b0a?. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft \\u1edf \\u0111\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 h\\u00e3y nh\\u1edb r\\u00f5 c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ec9 s\\u1ed1 c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh v\\u00e0 hi\\u1ec3u s\\u00e2u v\\u1ec1 n\\u00f3.\\\\n\\\\nB\\u1ea1n mang trong m\\u00ecnh r\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u \\u0111i\\u1ec3m m\\u1ea1nh. B\\u1ea1n l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n \\u0111\\u1ed9c l\\u1eadp tr\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi n\\u00e0y, kh\\u00f4ng c\\u1ea7n ph\\u1ea3i gi\\u1ed1ng ai v\\u00e0 c\\u0169ng kh\\u00f4ng c\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u00fd \\u0111\\u1ebfn \\u00e1nh nh\\u00ecn c\\u1ee7a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi kh\\u00e1c v\\u1ec1 m\\u00ecnh.\\\\n\\\\nQuan t\\u00e2m \\u0111\\u1ebfn nh\\u1eefng ch\\u1ec9 s\\u1ed1 l\\u00e0 \\u0111i\\u1ec3m h\\u1ea1n ch\\u1ebf c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n nh\\u01b0ng \\u0111\\u1eebng ch\\u0103m ch\\u0103m v\\u00e0o ch\\u00f